&lt;h1 id="the-list-of-n-things"&gt;The List of N Things&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;September 2009&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I bet you the current issue of Cosmopolitan has an article whose title begins with a number. &amp;ldquo;7 Things He Won&amp;rsquo;t Tell You about Sex,&amp;rdquo; or something like that. Some popular magazines feature articles of this type on the cover of every issue. That can&amp;rsquo;t be happening by accident. Editors must know they attract readers.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Users bring you traffic</title><link>https://linguista.cn/person/naval/orig/users-bring-you-traffic/</link><pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2008 18:07:08 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguista.cn/person/naval/orig/users-bring-you-traffic/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://linguista.cn/person/naval/zh/users-bring-you-traffic.zh/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
